830392e8e03b8e34490df87905873ffea0749f6d.query:
SELECT 
        start_time as "start_time!",
        end_time as "end_time!",
        resolution as "resolution!",
        market as "market!",
        open as "open!",
        close as "close!",
        high as "high!",
        low as "low!",
        volume as "volume!",
        complete as "complete!"
        from candles
        where market = $1
        and resolution = $2
        and complete = true
        ORDER BY start_time desc LIMIT 1

aa9adbbc7f215e28cc07b615f30ad9d3f415f252.query:
SELECT 
        start_time as "start_time!",
        end_time as "end_time!",
        resolution as "resolution!",
        market as "market!",
        open as "open!",
        close as "close!",
        high as "high!",
        low as "low!",
        volume as "volume!",
        complete as "complete!"
        from candles
        where market = $1
        and resolution = $2
        and start_time >= $3
        and end_time <= $4
        and complete = true
        ORDER BY start_time asc

b71ec8e5c041cec2c83778f31f7dc723cc1b5a8b.query:
SELECT 
         time as "time!",
         bid as "bid!",
         maker as "maker!",
         native_qty_paid as "native_qty_paid!",
         native_qty_received as "native_qty_received!",
         native_fee_or_rebate as "native_fee_or_rebate!" 
         from fills 
         where market = $1
         and time >= $2
         and time < $3 
         and maker = true
         ORDER BY time asc
